  <entry>
    <title>easy-langent_chapter6_note</title>
    <link href="/2026/04/25/easy-langent_chapter6_note/"/>
    <url>/2026/04/25/easy-langent_chapter6_note/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="案例三的优化："><a href="#案例三的优化：" class="headerlink" title="案例三的优化："></a>案例三的优化：</h2><h3 id="一：Promt，提示词上的优化"><a href="#一：Promt，提示词上的优化" class="headerlink" title="一：Promt，提示词上的优化"></a>一：Promt，提示词上的优化</h3><h4 id="第一个方向：优化节点内部的提示词"><a href="#第一个方向：优化节点内部的提示词" class="headerlink" title="第一个方向：优化节点内部的提示词"></a>第一个方向：优化节点内部的提示词</h4><p>在Ai节点都会有Promt空间，不同场景可以有更精确的Promt<br>比如optimize节点：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> user_feedback:<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 优化点1：提示词贴合汇报场景，明确要求（专业性、逻辑性、简洁度）</span><br>        prompt = PromptTemplate(<br>            input_variables=[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text&quot;</span>],<br>            template=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请优化以下项目进展汇报文本，面向领导汇报，要求：1. 保留核心信息（项目阶段、已完成工作、待推进事项、预计完成时间）；2. 提升专业性和逻辑性，分点清晰（无需列表，用文字衔接）；3. 语言简洁，避免冗余；4. 语气正式、严谨，符合职场汇报调性。优化完成后，单独一行以【优化理由：】开头给出1-2条简洁优化原因，重点说明贴合汇报场景的优化点。&quot;</span><br>        )<br>        chain = prompt | llm<br>        result = chain.invoke(&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text&quot;</span>: user_input&#125;).content<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>        <span class="hljs-comment"># 优化点2：结合用户反馈，强化汇报场景适配</span><br>        prompt = PromptTemplate(<br>            input_variables=[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;feedback&quot;</span>],<br>            template=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;根据用户反馈针对性优化项目进展汇报文本，面向领导汇报，严格保留核心信息（项目阶段、已完成工作、待推进事项、预计完成时间），重点贴合汇报场景：语气正式严谨、逻辑清晰、语言简洁。原文本：&#123;text&#125;\n用户反馈：&#123;feedback&#125;\n优化完成后，单独一行以【优化理由：】开头给出1-2条简洁优化原因，重点说明贴合汇报场景的优化点。&quot;</span><br>        )<br>        chain = prompt | llm<br>        result = chain.invoke(&#123;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text&quot;</span>: user_input, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;feedback&quot;</span>: user_feedback&#125;).content<br>```    <br><span class="hljs-comment">#### 第二个方向，修改反馈提示</span><br>在feedback_node，比如：<br>```python<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">feedback_node</span>(<span class="hljs-params">state: InteractiveOptState</span>) -&gt; InteractiveOptState:<br>    <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;&quot;【人机交互节点】展示结果+接收用户反馈，优化：提升交互流畅度，减少无效提问&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n&quot;</span> + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;-&quot;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">60</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;? AI优化后（汇报版）文本：&quot;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(state[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;optimized_text&quot;</span>])<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n? 优化建议/理由（贴合汇报场景）：&quot;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(state[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;optimize_suggest&quot;</span>])<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;\n&quot;</span> + <span class="hljs-string">&quot;-&quot;</span>*<span class="hljs-number">60</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 优化点3：补充反馈提示，引导用户精准反馈，减少无效输入</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;? 反馈提示：可输入「确认」（保留结果）、「修改」（需补充具体优化方向，例：更简洁/突出重点）、「退出」（终止流程）&quot;</span>)<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> <span class="hljs-literal">True</span>:<br>        user_feedback = <span class="hljs-built_in">input</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请输入反馈（严格按照提示输入）：&quot;</span>).strip()<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> user_feedback <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> [<span class="hljs-string">&quot;确认&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;修改&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;退出&quot;</span>]:<br><span class="hljs-comment">#优化点：用户输入「修改」时，引导补充具体需求，提升优化精准度</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> user_feedback == <span class="hljs-string">&quot;修改&quot;</span>:<br>                feedback_detail = <span class="hljs-built_in">input</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;请补充具体优化方向（例：更简洁、突出已完成工作、调整汇报语气）：&quot;</span>).strip()<br>                user_feedback = <span class="hljs-string">f&quot;修改：<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;feedback_detail&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span><br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;? 输入无效！请严格输入「确认」「修改」「退出」，无其他字符\n&quot;</span>)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-string">&quot;user_feedback&quot;</span>: user_feedback&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="二：给状态加轮次记录（智能体知道自己是第几轮优化）"><a href="#二：给状态加轮次记录（智能体知道自己是第几轮优化）" class="headerlink" title="二：给状态加轮次记录（智能体知道自己是第几轮优化）"></a>二：给状态加轮次记录（智能体知道自己是第几轮优化）</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">InteractiveOptState</span>(<span class="hljs-title class_ inherited__">TypedDict</span>):<br>    user_input: <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span><br>    optimized_text: <span class="hljs-type">Optional</span>[<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>]<br>    optimize_suggest: <span class="hljs-type">Optional</span>[<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>]<br>    user_feedback: <span class="hljs-type">Optional</span>[<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>]<br>    final_result: <span class="hljs-type">Optional</span>[<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>]<br>    optimize_round: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>  <span class="hljs-comment"># ? 新增：优化轮次（非Prompt优化）</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="三：自动异常捕获"><a href="#三：自动异常捕获" class="headerlink" title="三：自动异常捕获"></a>三：自动异常捕获</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">optimize_node</span>(<span class="hljs-params">state: InteractiveOptState</span>) -&gt; InteractiveOptState:<br>    user_input = state[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;user_input&quot;</span>]<br>    user_feedback = state[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;user_feedback&quot;</span>]<br>    current_round = state.get(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;optimize_round&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)  <span class="hljs-comment"># ? 获取轮次</span><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:  <span class="hljs-comment"># ? 异常捕获</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> user_feedback:<br>            prompt = PromptTemplate(...)<br>            chain = prompt | llm<br>            result = chain.invoke(...).content<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>            prompt = PromptTemplate(...)<br>            chain = prompt | llm<br>            result = chain.invoke(...).content<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> e:<br>        optimized_text = user_input<br>        optimize_suggest = <span class="hljs-string">f&quot;AI优化失败（<span class="hljs-subst">&#123;<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>(e)&#125;</span>），保留原文&quot;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-string">&quot;optimized_text&quot;</span>: optimized_text,<br>            <span class="hljs-string">&quot;optimize_suggest&quot;</span>: optimize_suggest,<br>            <span class="hljs-string">&quot;optimize_round&quot;</span>: current_round + <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>        &#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="四：自动保存结果到文件"><a href="#四：自动保存结果到文件" class="headerlink" title="四：自动保存结果到文件"></a>四：自动保存结果到文件</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">final_node</span>(<span class="hljs-params">state</span>):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;优化结果.txt&quot;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&quot;w&quot;</span>, encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> f:<br>        f.write(state[<span class="hljs-string">&quot;optimized_text&quot;</span>])<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># ? </span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ...<br>    一个比较实用的解决痛点的优化(*^_^*)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="未完待续…"><a href="#未完待续…" class="headerlink" title="未完待续…"></a>未完待续…</h3>]]></content>
    
    
